      "created_at": "2021-07-21T12:05:52.052Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Kur kete e thote The Guardian, (nje gazete e keqe persa i perket kinemase), i bie qe te jete e kunderta : “Titane” te kete qene vertet ndofta filmi më i mire i festivalit (ose nder më te miret).</p>\n<p>Ose thene ndryshe : çeshte nje film i mire? Nje film qe ka guts (këllqe)</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/jul/17/cannes-2021-titane-didnt-deserve-the-palme-but-it-had-guts-drive-and-an-anthro-automotive-hybrid-devil-child\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/6/1/612be4ec55bc0d3e7f59d04f76d02b9da2867791.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/jul/17/cannes-2021-titane-didnt-deserve-the-palme-but-it-had-guts-drive-and-an-anthro-automotive-hybrid-devil-child\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"08:21PM - 17 July 2021\">the Guardian – 17 Jul 21</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <span class=\"broken-image\" title=\"This image is broken\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-unlink svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#unlink\"></use></svg></span>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/jul/17/cannes-2021-titane-didnt-deserve-the-palme-but-it-had-guts-drive-and-an-anthro-automotive-hybrid-devil-child\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Titane may not have been the best film at Cannes, but it had guts, drive –...</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Julia Ducournau has became the second woman ever to win the Palme d’Or at Cannes. Her triumph is a suitably rock’n’roll ending for this year’s festival</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
