      "created_at": "2021-07-25T06:51:51.365Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Metrazhi i parë i shkurter (2011) i fitueses se Palmes se Arte në Cannes në 2021:</p>\n<div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"k2qGf8FZK2A\" data-video-title=\"WATCH Cannes Palme d'Or winner Julia Ducournau's first short film &quot;Junior&quot;\" data-video-start-time=\"\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2qGf8FZK2A\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-thumbnail\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/0/c/0c91ad31bb6919fa35b86072362b76cd0b71d345.jpeg\" title=\"WATCH Cannes Palme d'Or winner Julia Ducournau's first short film &quot;Junior&quot;\" data-dominant-color=\"797174\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
