      "post_number": 10,
      "username": "InkuizitoriMoth",
      "name": "..... ......",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/inkuizitorimoth/{size}/7035_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-10-24T21:32:49.290Z",
      "cooked": "<p>film alkimist ne kerkim te gurit filosofal qe sipas prrallave te alkimisteve do i ktheje te gjithe metalet ne ar. Pra film mesjetar, obskurantist, injorance fetare, alkimia eshte mesjetare, ndersa kimia moderne. Tabela e Mendelejevit nuk e pranon alkimine, te gjithe elemente e tabeles jane veç e veç, nuk konvertohen ne njeri tjetrin.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 119549,
      "post_number": 11,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-10-25T07:34:02.992Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Në thelb (po ta mendosh mire), eshte film tarantinian, sidomos gjysma e parë.</p>\n<p>Gjysma e dyte (“hyrja” në skenë e Vincent, shefit te zjarrfiksave), eshte më e mire (më personale), padyshim falë personazhit te Vincent:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/1/1/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/1/1/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158_2_400x225.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"2uRh3uWygzHlvTOEN9fmP6uIe2A\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/1/1/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158_2_400x225.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/1/1/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158_2_600x337.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/1/1/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158_2_800x450.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/1/1/11815cd3c79b6c67f7d0c475a517d6f51fa2b158_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1280×720 77.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>ps: kur ti thua qe nuk eshte film i merzitshem, per mendimin tim, ti don te thuash qe eshte film qe më së shumti shokon (surprizon) se sa emocionon (dhe nuk e thua ‘i merzitshem’ siç do thoshte nje spektator lambda per nje film, per shembull, te Michelangelo Antonionit), apo jo ?</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 9,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 119551,
      "post_number": 12,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-10-25T08:29:17.937Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Insistoja tek influlenca Tarantiniane si regji (besoj se eshte më e forta, më prezentja, në kinematografine e 20-25 vitet e fundit, sidomos tek ajo qe desheron te konsiderohet si autoriale, personale) sepse, perndryshe, “Titane” ka që ç’ke me të referencat (<strong>citimet</strong>) e tij kinematografike:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>“Christine” - te John Carpenter (1983)</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/e/4/e4726b4f32c13a2fb568ed781dc27f96e684aa0e.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"wAW0k3PC6tjfgkK0PAwK1gkZepM\" width=\"220\" height=\"325\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/7/a/7ae7d6c31895f62ca641878c194e855da7be9345.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"hxgXLwYP8ojGURVYqxPMDgdyUg5\" width=\"266\" height=\"112\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>“Crash” te David Cronenberg (1996)</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/3/5/35835f8499010621452ded6aa62170621627f5bc.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"7DoLPNktNgCzLM4WtfTiMd9mMA4\" width=\"220\" height=\"327\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/c/9/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/9/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232_2_400x241.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"sOVBmUAviX0nghcNnf6joMgdBPI\" width=\"400\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/9/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232_2_400x241.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/9/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232_2_600x361.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/9/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232_2_800x482.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/9/c9feabe77e311cf46a6f419968f8c49f90f22232_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1791×1080 173 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>“2001: A Space Odyssey” te Kubrick, 1968</strong> (per lindjen e nje Njerezimi te Ri në fund te filmit)<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/2/0/206f18b83d6b7ac6c0461ace80dcd00d4d59be7d.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"4CViKbSXzULsTPPb74jffDvZ44d\" width=\"220\" height=\"329\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/0/c/0c84ae366934dbe8e65a1c5d30530d9f4c099ad9.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"1MJZLWAjgkwOYgieXAjMQnzXTap\" width=\"266\" height=\"122\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>e mbi te gjitha, <strong>saga e Alienëve</strong> :</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>“Alien” (Ridley Scott, 1979)<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/b/e/be442129e379ffb33a3369194b42f1203625f084.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"r9aGxZJs9Hewj6w2mALv60Fwdbm\" width=\"266\" height=\"113\"></p>\n<p><strong>+</strong></p>\n<p>“Aliens” (James Camerun, 1986)<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/a/d/ad1ee3e2e4ff991d350d1397b2a4efd272619cd0.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"oHuMCPsx2g6axdxaDQkuZO0u4Uw\" width=\"350\" height=\"188\"></p>\n<p><strong>+</strong></p>\n<p>“Alein 3” (David Fincher, 1992)<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/0/3/03e8229f3d35a32600d61138276765cb403d4c71.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"yyMlPRzwBTY08xwNVJW8xVvsPL\" width=\"266\" height=\"114\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 9,
      "like_count": 0
    },
